1
00:01:21,491 --> 00:01:26,850
[Love Endures]

2
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,500
[Episode 30]

3
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:58,120
Yifei,

4
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,079
is that really you?

5
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:03,480
I dreamed every day,

6
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,840
and I always dreamed of you.

7
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:08,198
But you weren't there anymore

8
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:10,000
when I woke up.

9
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:14,079
I kept asking myself

10
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:17,000
where you have been.

11
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:21,319
But I just found out

12
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:26,800
that I've lost you a long time ago.

13
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,520
Yifei...

14
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,919
Yifei,

15
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,560
I'm too daft.

16
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:38,919
If I hadn't left you

17
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,080
to buy potato chips then,

18
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:44,400
would that stop you
from doing what you did?

19
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:45,840
Stop blaming yourself.

20
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,039
I don't blame you at all.

21
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,560
We were all too young

22
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,879
at that time.

23
00:02:52,319 --> 00:02:53,198
We were not brave enough,

24
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,439
and we didn't know how to face things.

25
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,639
So

26
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,918
that was my own choice.

27
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,800
I don't blame you at all.

28
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,719
It's on me.

29
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,479
It's all my fault!

30
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:06,399
If only I hadn't left

31
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,919
and kept you company then,

32
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,919
you wouldn't have taken your life.

33
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:12,919
If I gave you a hand at that time,

34
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:16,520
we would be growing up together.

35
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:21,159
You would forget the negative things

36
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:24,159
and fulfill your dream.

37
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,400
You would also get married

38
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,680
and have children with the man you love.

39
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:33,960
It's all my fault!

40
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,240
It's not.

41
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,680
Yingzi,

42
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,280
do you still remember

43
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,719
what I told you?

44
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,519
I have

45
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:42,918
always felt

46
00:03:43,199 --> 00:03:44,319
that I'm never a fortunate person,

47
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:46,000
unlike you guys

48
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:48,960
who have parents who love you.

49
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,199
I have always

50
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,360
envied you guys,

51
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,360
but

52
00:03:54,719 --> 00:03:55,759
things are different now.

53
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:57,399
I have my father, my mother,

54
00:03:57,719 --> 00:04:00,120
and my grandmother who love me

55
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,599
over here.

56
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,280
Everything I wanted before

57
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,759
has all been realized here.

58
00:04:07,393 --> 00:04:08,233
So

59
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,439
don't worry about me.

60
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:12,319
I'm having a really good time here.

61
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,199
All these years,

62
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:16,959
you bear

63
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,600
too many of my wishes.

64
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,759
It's time to let go.

65
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,279
There are so many people who love you

66
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,759
in the world,

67
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,639
they are all waiting for you.

68
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:30,279
Please get well soon.

69
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,600
But, Yifei,

70
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:46,079
are you leaving me again?

71
00:04:55,959 --> 00:04:57,639
Stay, okay?

72
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,720
As long as

73
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:01,399
your heart is

74
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,240
always thinking of me,

75
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:05,240
I will forever

76
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,720
and always

77
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:09,920
be with you.

78
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,879
Do you remember

79
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:16,920
that game we played together

80
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,199
when we were kids?

81
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:21,199
Yes.

82
00:05:22,279 --> 00:05:24,319
Let's play again, shall we?

83
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:26,800
Sure.

84
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,360
As long as you think of me,

85
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,240
I will always be here.

86
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:44,920
Yingzi,

87
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,879
return to your world.

88
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,519
(Treat this as a little promise)

89
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,800
for our thirties, alright?

90
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,399
I'm the witness.

91
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:19,720
Pinky promise.

92
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:22,399
Pinky promise.

93
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:24,519
Stamped.

94
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,279
(Yingzi,)

95
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,879
(in fact,)

96
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,920
(although people leave,)

97
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,000
(as long as you)

98
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,360
(always,)

99
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:36,959
(always have her in your heart,)

100
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,680
(she will always be there.)

101
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,560
Bye now.

102
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,079
(Bye.)

103
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:10,600
For so many years

104
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,319
you have been hiding
somewhere I can't see,

105
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,279
pretending to be Yifei,

106
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,040
because you wanted to keep me company.

107
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,639
Yes.

108
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,879
I have been waiting

109
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,439
for a better time to tell you.

110
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:30,160
So you thought of

111
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,519
the game?

112
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,399
I have no other choice.

113
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,000
I only know this.

114
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,960
If this method fails,

115
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:48,120
I will keep looking

116
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,720
until it works.

117
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:54,480
What if you keep looking
but you can't find any solution?

118
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,159
Do you want to never see me again
for the rest of your life?

119
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:07,200
Actually, when I saw you in my vision

120
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:11,000
when I was making the game,

121
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,439
I often wonder

122
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,600
how you'll react

123
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,679
when you see all these.

124
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:23,000
However, as I thought about it,

125
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,240
I became a little afraid to meet you

126
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,879
because I was afraid
you couldn't accept it,

127
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,120
I was even more afraid
that you would forget me.

128
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:36,440
I'm the one who should apologize.

129
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:38,159
All these years,

130
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,080
I had no idea what happened.

131
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:45,240
I've been blaming you
for hiding this from me.

132
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,080
I even blamed you for so many years

133
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,720
because I didn't hear from you at all.

134
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,519
I've been living happily

135
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,759
in my imaginative world

136
00:09:58,159 --> 00:10:01,000
when you were keeping
this secret from me.

137
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,080
It must be very hard for you.

138
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:11,159
Not at all.

139
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,120
For you,

140
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,960
I'm willing to do anything.

141
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:15,000
Yifei, I'm late.

142
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:17,799
Sorry,

143
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:20,360
I only came to see you now.

144
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:25,759
I brought you your favorite lilies.

145
00:11:37,919 --> 00:11:39,039
I'm not crying.

146
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:45,679
Yifei,

147
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:48,600
it's been a long time
since you saw me, right?

148
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:50,759
What do you think?

149
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:53,039
Have I changed?

150
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,759
Although you weren't around

151
00:11:58,399 --> 00:11:59,759
these years,

152
00:12:00,879 --> 00:12:03,120
I always felt like I was dreaming

153
00:12:03,759 --> 00:12:05,159
with you around.

154
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:08,679
(Whenever I was sad, upset,)

155
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,840
(or encountering difficulties,)

156
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:13,039
(it felt like you were there
encouraging me.)

157
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:15,879
Yifei,

158
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:19,600
I'm a reporter now.

159
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,720
Although I'm not really excellent yet,

160
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,159
I fulfilled my childhood dream

161
00:12:30,759 --> 00:12:33,080
and the promise we made at that time.

162
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:34,960
I'm awesome, right?

163
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,480
I've been alright,

164
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,519
you do not need to worry.

165
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,039
Over the years,

166
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:44,679
everyone together has woven
a very beautiful dream for me.

167
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:50,039
In hindsight,

168
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:52,559
I was pretty useless.

169
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:55,439
I didn't do anything for anyone.

170
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,519
Yifei, I won't cry anymore.

171
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:09,720
Do not worry.

172
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:12,480
I've moved on.

173
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,240
I just...

174
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:23,759
I just miss you a little.

175
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:34,120
How are you doing over there?

176
00:13:37,919 --> 00:13:39,679
Have you become

177
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:41,480
a great dancer?

178
00:13:44,399 --> 00:13:45,360
I'm sure no one bullies you anymore

179
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:49,120
over there.

180
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,679
If you miss me,

181
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,200
you should come to my dream for fun.

182
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:11,480
You can tell me

183
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,159
what you want to eat and do.

184
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:16,120
I'll make it happen, okay?

185
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:25,840
Yifei,

186
00:14:28,759 --> 00:14:29,759
do not worry.

187
00:14:35,639 --> 00:14:36,919
I'll be fine.

188
00:14:37,919 --> 00:14:39,319
We will all be fine.

189
00:14:44,879 --> 00:14:46,159
It's getting late,

190
00:14:47,039 --> 00:14:48,439
they are all waiting for me.

191
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,240
I'll take off first.

192
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,559
I will come to see you often
in the future.

193
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:59,519
Bye, Yifei.

194
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:20,720
Let's go.

195
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:24,720
Yingzi, do you still remember this?

196
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:29,519
Isn't this the point-and-shoot camera
that Yifei gave us

197
00:15:29,519 --> 00:15:31,200
during our graduation?

198
00:15:31,639 --> 00:15:33,039
This is what she left for you.

199
00:15:33,759 --> 00:15:37,000
I haven't had the chance
to show this to you these years.

200
00:15:38,159 --> 00:15:39,399
It's time to check it out.

201
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,320
(Yifei, didn't you say
even dummies can use)

202
00:16:03,559 --> 00:16:04,360
(a point-and-shoot camera?)

203
00:16:05,679 --> 00:16:06,439
(Click on this.)

204
00:16:07,039 --> 00:16:07,399
(It's filming.)

205
00:16:07,799 --> 00:16:08,639
(It started filming already.)

206
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:09,600
(It's filming.)

207
00:16:09,759 --> 00:16:11,000
(What does this mean?)

208
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,039
(This can only mean)

209
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:13,639
(you are worse than a dummy.)

210
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,559
(Well, it's already filming.)

211
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:21,080
(Let's all say one thing to this camera)

212
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,840
(and to our thirty-year-old selves.)

213
00:16:23,159 --> 00:16:24,720
(What kind of trick are you
playing now?)

214
00:16:24,919 --> 00:16:25,559
(Right.)

215
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,320
(It's like we have to write an essay
for an exam.)

216
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,919
(I think this is a pretty good idea.)

217
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:32,720
(Let's film this down.)

218
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,000
(This will be memorable.)

219
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,639
(Each of us will keep one copy,)

220
00:16:35,639 --> 00:16:37,320
(and we'll take it out again
when we're 30.)

221
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:37,960
(How meaningful would that be?)

222
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:38,840
(That's right.)

223
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:39,960
(You understand me well.)

224
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,000
(Let me think.)

225
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:41,879
(I need to think about it.)

226
00:16:41,879 --> 00:16:43,039
(I'll go first.)

227
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:50,039
(Hello, 30-year-old Huang Yingzi.)

228
00:16:50,039 --> 00:16:52,679
(Not expecting to see me here, are you?)

229
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:55,679
(At 30,)

230
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:58,240
(you must have become
a very famous journalist.)

231
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,639
(There is no justice
that you cannot deliver)

232
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:01,240
(and no truth that you cannot discover.)

233
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,679
(Let all the bad guys
have nowhere to hide.)

234
00:17:03,919 --> 00:17:05,639
(Is this what a reporter should say?)

235
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,720
(It sounds so much
like you're quoting One Piece.)

236
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,680
(Shush. I'm not done yet.)

237
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,720
(I believe that when I'm 30,)

238
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,920
(these friends around me)

239
00:17:15,519 --> 00:17:17,039
(will still keep you company.)

240
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:19,519
(No, it should be over 30.)

241
00:17:19,519 --> 00:17:20,920
(When we're all 80,)

242
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,799
(we'll still be together always.)

243
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,279
(I hope that we won't)

244
00:17:26,279 --> 00:17:27,640
(be forced by you to do
dumb things like this anymore)

245
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:29,440
(when we're 80.)

246
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,519
(Fine, you can speak now, right?)

247
00:17:31,519 --> 00:17:32,240
(You are the next one.)

248
00:17:32,519 --> 00:17:34,920
(Zhuang Yuan!)

249
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:36,480
(I'll do the interview.)

250
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,079
(Zhuang Yuan,)

251
00:17:37,079 --> 00:17:38,799
(why do you sit inside this tire)

252
00:17:38,799 --> 00:17:40,799
(every time you come to the rooftop?)

253
00:17:41,319 --> 00:17:42,639
(That's because I like this tire.)

254
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,359
May I ask if you can actually drink

255
00:17:44,359 --> 00:17:46,559
(from this straw?)

256
00:17:46,559 --> 00:17:47,639
(It doesn't matter if I can't,)

257
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,960
(the important thing is to have fun.)

258
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:52,160
Are you using this tactic

259
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,640
(to attract girls around you?)

260
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,640
(Fine!)

261
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,799
I'll film.

262
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,319
Thirty-year-old Zhuang Yuan,

263
00:18:00,319 --> 00:18:01,680
I think

264
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,720
you have become a professor
by that time, right?

265
00:18:04,119 --> 00:18:05,839
No, not necessarily a professor,

266
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,400
(just do what you like,)

267
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:07,799
(and that'll suffice.)

268
00:18:08,799 --> 00:18:09,879
Zhuang Yuan is awesome!

269
00:18:10,519 --> 00:18:11,359
(Zhuang Yuan!)

270
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:12,880
(Next.)

271
00:18:12,880 --> 00:18:13,839
(I've thought about it.)

272
00:18:14,319 --> 00:18:15,000
(Mingyu!)

273
00:18:15,720 --> 00:18:16,680
(Is this alright?)

274
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:17,279
Yes.

275
00:18:17,279 --> 00:18:18,319
I'll make you appear slimmer.

276
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,599
Just my face will suffice.

277
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:20,359
Sure.

278
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,200
Hello, 30-year-old Fang Mingyu.

279
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:27,440
(I don't know where you are)

280
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,640
(and what you are doing,)

281
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,599
(I have to leave you with a question.)

282
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,680
(Are you happy now?)

283
00:18:34,279 --> 00:18:35,480
(I'll be waiting for
your beautiful reply.)

284
00:18:36,599 --> 00:18:37,079
(Alright.)

285
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,359
