418
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:33,519
(Guan Chao,)

419
00:23:37,319 --> 00:23:38,680
please be happy.

420
00:23:57,119 --> 00:23:57,839
Mingyu,

421
00:23:59,519 --> 00:24:03,200
