425
00:24:11,519 --> 00:24:12,160
Zhuang Yuan,

426
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,319
our academic overachiever,

427
00:24:16,359 --> 00:24:19,039
the life coach of Six of Hangtian City,

428
00:24:20,079 --> 00:24:21,159
(it is a pity)

429
00:24:22,039 --> 00:24:23,440
(that I won't have a chance)

430
00:24:24,319 --> 00:24:26,399
(to hear your life philosophies
anymore.)

431
00:24:28,519 --> 00:24:30,920
However, those dummies need you
very much.

432
00:24:32,319 --> 00:24:33,759
So after I left,

433
00:24:34,759 --> 00:24:36,000
please don't break down.

434
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,079
Jiang Yi,

435
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:43,359
although you are not with us now,

436
00:24:45,880 --> 00:24:47,440
I will tell you secretly

437
00:24:49,519 --> 00:24:50,559
(that Huang Yingzi)

438
00:24:52,119 --> 00:24:54,399
(actually misses you very much.)

439
00:24:57,359 --> 00:24:59,599
(So after I left,)

440
00:24:59,799 --> 00:25:01,799
(if there's anyone who can
accompany her on my behalf,)

441
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:03,400
(that person has to be you.)

442
00:25:03,759 --> 00:25:04,920
(You can definitely do it,)

443
00:25:05,559 --> 00:25:06,160
(Yingzi,)

444
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:09,079
(don't cry.)

445
00:25:10,446 --> 00:25:13,686
(You are the one
I worry about the most.)

446
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:17,480
(However,)

447
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:21,759
(I still selfishly made this decision.)

448
00:25:23,599 --> 00:25:27,119
(You must never blame yourself.)

449
00:25:28,079 --> 00:25:29,559
(I'll leave
all the ups and downs of my life)

450
00:25:30,799 --> 00:25:32,639
(in this summer,)

451
00:25:34,079 --> 00:25:35,000
(but)

452
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:42,519
(I still have many things left to do.)

453
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:47,119
(I still have many dreams
that have not come true.)

454
00:25:47,400 --> 00:25:50,039
(You have to take my place)

455
00:25:50,839 --> 00:25:52,200
(by living well)

456
00:25:53,559 --> 00:25:54,799
(and helping me finish them.)

457
00:25:57,119 --> 00:25:58,119
(As for you,)

458
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:03,920
(you have to realize your dream, too.)

459
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:06,440
(You must be bold)

460
00:26:07,039 --> 00:26:08,519
(in loving someone
who also loves you very much.)

461
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:10,440
(Do not ever forget)

462
00:26:11,839 --> 00:26:14,159
(that you are Huang Yingzi
from Hangtian City,)

463
00:26:16,839 --> 00:26:19,240
(the forever sunshine of the six of us.)

464
00:26:32,559 --> 00:26:35,960
Alright, friends.

465
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,160
(Bye now,)

466
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:52,359
(my friends.)

467
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,960
We have waited for this day
for far too long.

468
00:27:13,319 --> 00:27:16,319
Yes, way too long.

469
00:27:20,839 --> 00:27:22,319
We finally made it.

470
00:27:54,319 --> 00:27:55,119
What's wrong?

471
00:27:56,559 --> 00:27:57,200
Nothing.

472
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,920
You've looked troubled
since you got home.

473
00:28:02,359 --> 00:28:03,679
You didn't eat much food either.

474
00:28:04,119 --> 00:28:06,519
What's up? Do you think I can't see it?

475
00:28:13,319 --> 00:28:14,319
Yingzi is back.

476
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:18,000
We went to visit Yifei together.

477
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:25,000
How is Yingzi?

478
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,799
She finally stepped out of it,

479
00:28:30,519 --> 00:28:33,920
we can finally let it go.

480
00:28:35,799 --> 00:28:36,279
Chao,

481
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:38,160
from now on,

482
00:28:39,079 --> 00:28:40,359
if you miss her,

483
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:43,799
I will follow you to visit her.

484
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,680
Thank you, Yang Fan.

485
00:28:49,799 --> 00:28:51,440
We are family.

486
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:52,720
Why so courteous?

487
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,720
Since Yifei's departure,

488
00:29:02,519 --> 00:29:03,640
my father left, too.

489
00:29:04,920 --> 00:29:06,799
I used to think that I was
the most unfortunate person

490
00:29:08,045 --> 00:29:09,045
in the world

491
00:29:12,279 --> 00:29:13,480
until I met you.

492
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,559
We even have a child together.

493
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:20,160
I finally think

494
00:29:21,319 --> 00:29:22,480
the world

495
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:24,559
turns out to be fair.

496
00:29:42,079 --> 00:29:42,599
Hello?

497
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:48,880
Alright.

498
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:50,519
Thanks.

499
00:29:56,799 --> 00:29:57,559
What's wrong?

500
00:30:01,559 --> 00:30:02,960
Grandma is not in good health.

501
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:08,759
Look at all of you making such a fuss.

502
00:30:08,759 --> 00:30:10,759
It was just a fall.

503
00:30:11,079 --> 00:30:12,879
I was even rushed to the hospital.

504
00:30:14,079 --> 00:30:15,919
Why didn't you listen?

505
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,759
The doctor said you're not allowed
to be discharged,

506
00:30:17,759 --> 00:30:19,119
but you just had to flee.

507
00:30:19,599 --> 00:30:21,799
I can't get used to the hospital bed.

508
00:30:21,799 --> 00:30:23,799
As soon as I open my eyes,
I see a blank white wall.

509
00:30:23,799 --> 00:30:26,000
People come to check on me every time.

510
00:30:26,279 --> 00:30:27,079
How uncomfortable.

511
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:30,720
Grandma, we have to follow
the doctor's orders.

512
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:34,200
I know my own body,

513
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:36,839
it's no big deal.

514
00:30:36,839 --> 00:30:39,559
The doctor just likes scaring me.

515
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:42,000
Grandma, don't worry.

516
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:43,079
Just leave the wanton shop

517
00:30:43,079 --> 00:30:44,240
to us from now on.

518
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:46,200
You, just go home and have a good rest.

519
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,920
You are all lecturing me.

520
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:49,960
If I rest,

521
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:51,559
who will make you wontons?

522
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:53,599
You don't come back often,

523
00:30:53,599 --> 00:30:55,159
how can you go back
with empty stomachs?

524
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:58,920
I was lying on the hospital bed

525
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:00,079
when I thought

526
00:31:01,559 --> 00:31:03,319
life and death are up to fate.

527
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:06,359
If something really went wrong
after the fall,

528
00:31:07,119 --> 00:31:08,720
that is my destiny.

529
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:13,160
It's no use being cautious.

530
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,440
No, Grandma.

531
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,519
Touch wood.

532
00:31:15,519 --> 00:31:17,400
Guan Chao's child isn't born yet,

533
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:19,200
you haven't become
a great-grandmother yet.

534
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:20,480
How could you say such a thing?

535
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:22,400
Grandma, he's right.

536
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,559
And we

537
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:25,039
haven't even gotten married yet.

538
00:31:25,039 --> 00:31:27,359
You have to be there for us
as we get married and have children.

539
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:28,759
You have to give us red envelopes.

540
00:31:30,359 --> 00:31:31,639
Indeed.

541
00:31:31,640 --> 00:31:33,039
All of you are aware of this.

542
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:36,200
Grandma,

543
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:38,000
what do you want to do

544
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:39,039
if the wonton shop
is closed for a few days?

545
00:31:43,319 --> 00:31:47,559
Well, I used to want
to do a lot of things.

546
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:51,799
I wanted to travel and have adventures

547
00:31:52,839 --> 00:31:57,639
but I stayed in Hangtian City
for close to a lifetime now.

548
00:31:58,799 --> 00:32:02,559
I got old as I stayed here.

549
00:32:08,359 --> 00:32:09,439
Grandma,

550
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:12,039
isn't it a pity

551
00:32:12,039 --> 00:32:13,440
that you never left Hangtian City?

552
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,680
I just hope

553
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:21,880
all of you can live
different lives from mine.

554
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:24,440
Just seeing you all live well

555
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:27,359
makes my life complete.

556
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,559
Why didn't you tell us

557
00:32:44,559 --> 00:32:45,960
about Grandma's condition?

558
00:32:47,799 --> 00:32:49,200
She is afraid that you will worry

559
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,440
so she specially asked me

560
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:51,799
to hide it from you.

561
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:52,839
It's all my fault.

562
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:56,039
She wouldn't have fallen

563
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,799
if I stayed with her all the time.

564
00:33:00,119 --> 00:33:01,359
Don't think that way.

565
00:33:03,799 --> 00:33:05,079
Grandma is old.

566
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:06,720
It's not your fault.

567
00:33:08,559 --> 00:33:11,279
When I was little, I used to think
Grandma was like a superwoman.

568
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:14,000
It's like whenever we talk to her
about something,

569
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:17,359
she would assure us that it's fine

570
00:33:17,359 --> 00:33:18,919
and help us solve it.

571
00:33:19,759 --> 00:33:21,160
I always thought

572
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,359
when I become capable,

573
00:33:23,799 --> 00:33:25,079
I'll be good to her.

574
00:33:26,720 --> 00:33:28,519
Now that we are all capable,

575
00:33:30,839 --> 00:33:32,440
Grandma does not have much time left.

576
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:35,599
Let's

577
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:37,160
stop feeling bad here.

578
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:39,359
We should think about

579
00:33:40,079 --> 00:33:42,079
what we can do for her

580
00:33:43,319 --> 00:33:44,639
in her remaining time.

581
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:48,319
What else can we do?

582
00:33:50,599 --> 00:33:52,599
Have you already forgotten
what she just said?

583
00:33:59,359 --> 00:34:00,119
(Grandma,)

584
00:34:00,119 --> 00:34:02,039
don't you want to leave Hangtian City?

585
00:34:02,039 --> 00:34:04,240
We came up with an itinerary
for you overnight.

586
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:05,200
Jiang Yi, tell us about it.

587
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:05,720
Right.

588
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:07,160
This is it.

589
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,280
Grandma, look.

590
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:10,079
This is Jiuzhai Valley.

591
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:12,480
This is Yulong Snow Mountain.

592
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:14,280
This is Xi Lake.

593
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,519
This is Huangguoshu Waterfall.

594
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:19,440
My arms and legs are old,

595
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,320
can I still visit so many places?

596
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,518
You're not old at all.

597
00:34:22,518 --> 00:34:24,678
I was thinking of taking you
to ride elephants in Thailand.

598
00:34:25,199 --> 00:34:26,119
Elephants are huge,

599
00:34:26,119 --> 00:34:27,800
I wouldn't dare to climb up.

600
00:34:28,518 --> 00:34:30,678
Fine, let's play it safe, then.

601
00:34:30,679 --> 00:34:31,480
Huangpu River.

602
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:32,599
What do you think about Huangpu River?

603
00:34:33,719 --> 00:34:34,719
Aren't you used to love

604
00:34:34,719 --> 00:34:35,960
watching "The Bund" the most?

605
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:37,000
Huangpu River sounds good.

606
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:38,559
Huangpu River sounds good.

607
00:34:38,559 --> 00:34:39,519
Huangpu River is good.

608
00:34:40,119 --> 00:34:42,039
Let's go straight north after Shanghai.

609
00:34:42,039 --> 00:34:44,159
Let's go see the Great Wall

610
00:34:44,159 --> 00:34:45,119
and Tiananmen.

611
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:46,519
Let me check.

612
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:49,159
We can go to Hulunbuir Prairie straight,

613
00:34:49,159 --> 00:34:50,480
and finally Yunnan.

614
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,400
The weather

615
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:53,239
and temperature there are ideal.

616
00:34:53,239 --> 00:34:55,199
You can stay there
for as long as you want.

617
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:59,079
You want me
to travel across the country?

618
00:34:59,079 --> 00:35:00,960
That's not really enough.

619
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,039
After traveling all over the country,

620
00:35:02,039 --> 00:35:03,199
we'll take you
to travel around the world.

621
00:35:05,360 --> 00:35:06,800
That's great.

622
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,119
I must visit

623
00:35:08,119 --> 00:35:10,760
all the places I haven't been to
in one go.

624
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:11,519
Do not worry.

625
00:35:11,519 --> 00:35:12,638
No matter where you want to go,

626
00:35:12,639 --> 00:35:13,760
we'll keep you company.

627
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:18,559
Grandma, do you remember?

628
00:35:19,039 --> 00:35:20,840
The first time we left Hangtian City

629
00:35:20,840 --> 00:35:22,159
was because of you.

630
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,480
Yingzi.

631
00:35:44,239 --> 00:35:45,239
Are you working hard?

632
00:35:48,199 --> 00:35:49,320
Remember to take breaks.

633
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,159
Got it.

634
00:36:16,639 --> 00:36:18,000
Look. Do you see it?

635
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:18,679
This is

636
00:36:18,679 --> 00:36:20,800
where Stephanie Sun will have
her Beijing concert.

637
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,920
It would be great
if we were born in Beijing.

638
00:36:22,920 --> 00:36:24,400
Not only could we watch the concert,

639
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:25,480
we could also watch the Olympics.

640
00:36:26,719 --> 00:36:29,159
I have always wanted to
go to Qingbei University.

641
00:36:29,159 --> 00:36:31,320
I heard the campus is pretty nice.

642
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:33,159
I haven't had a chance to see it.

643
00:36:33,159 --> 00:36:35,039
Besides, there is a National Library
in Beijing

644
00:36:35,039 --> 00:36:36,679
with more books than you can read
in a lifetime in there.

645
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:40,519
Stop grabbing my hair.

646
00:36:40,519 --> 00:36:42,479
The Olympic Games are about to start.

647
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,719
I, the future world champion,

648
00:36:44,719 --> 00:36:46,800
don't even know where the entrance
of National Stadium is.

649
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:49,719
Right, we have never left Hangtian City.

650
00:36:49,719 --> 00:36:51,760
We don't know what big cities

651
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,199
like Beijing and Shanghai are like.

652
00:36:53,199 --> 00:36:54,400
We only saw them on the television.

653
00:36:58,519 --> 00:36:59,479
Want to go to Beijing?

654
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,159
Isn't that simple?

655
00:37:01,559 --> 00:37:02,800
Let's just go.

656
00:37:10,039 --> 00:37:11,840
Us? To Beijing?

657
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:16,159
I really do want to go there.

658
00:37:17,559 --> 00:37:20,599
We actually want to go, too.

659
00:37:20,599 --> 00:37:21,679
If you want to go to Beijing,

660
00:37:21,679 --> 00:37:22,920
don't count me in.

661
00:37:22,920 --> 00:37:24,320
I'm not interested.

662
00:37:27,159 --> 00:37:27,920
Why?

663
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,000
If all of us are really

664
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:31,239
going to Beijing

665
00:37:31,239 --> 00:37:32,559
and leaving you in Hangtian City alone,

666
00:37:32,559 --> 00:37:33,679
are you going to cry out of jealousy?

667
00:37:34,039 --> 00:37:35,000
Right, Jiang Yi.

668
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:35,599
Let's go.

669
00:37:35,599 --> 00:37:36,199
Six of Hangtian City

670
00:37:36,199 --> 00:37:38,000
wouldn't be complete without you.

671
00:37:38,400 --> 00:37:40,360
Let's not talk about Beijing first.

672
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:41,639
I have one question.

673
00:37:41,639 --> 00:37:43,039
Do you have money

674
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,239
to travel to Beijing?

675
00:37:52,079 --> 00:37:54,320
Sir, how much for
the leopard coral grouper?

676
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:55,039
I usually sell these

677
00:37:55,039 --> 00:37:57,079
for 148 yuan per pound.

678
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:59,000
I'll make it 140 yuan per pound for you.

679
00:38:00,119 --> 00:38:01,360
It is what it is.

680
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,599
Pick a big one for me.

681
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:03,480
Sure.

682
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:06,400
That's quite generous.

683
00:38:08,480 --> 00:38:10,679
It's not an easy job, they get up early
and stay up late at night.

684
00:38:10,679 --> 00:38:12,079
We can't take advantage of them.

685
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:16,280
Look at that old lady
selling duck eggs.

686
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,800
She had to spend a huge amount
because she was sick.

687
00:38:18,119 --> 00:38:19,760
Wang who sells tofu

688
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:21,639
also needs money
to send his brother to college.

689
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:25,039
Zhang who sells pork...

690
00:38:31,159 --> 00:38:31,800
What's up with Zhang?

691
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:32,599
Just say it.

692
00:38:32,599 --> 00:38:34,320
Don't keep me in suspense.

693
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:39,079
He lost thousands of yuan
buying lottery tickets.

694
00:38:39,079 --> 00:38:40,039
If his wife found out,

695
00:38:40,039 --> 00:38:40,760
Hangtian City

696
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:42,920
would see another bloody storm.

697
00:38:46,239 --> 00:38:48,840
Dad, you are eager to help others.

698
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:51,159
You should also sponsor your daughter.

699
00:38:52,760 --> 00:38:55,039
Crabs, oysters, red king crab,

700
00:38:55,039 --> 00:38:56,639
take whichever one you like.

701
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,840
I don't want these.

702
00:39:00,679 --> 00:39:02,559
Stationery, CDs, extracurricular books,

703
00:39:02,559 --> 00:39:03,960
these are nothing.

704
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:06,360
No, I don't want these.

705
00:39:07,079 --> 00:39:08,559
Aren't those what you like?

706
00:39:08,559 --> 00:39:10,280
What's the matter? What do you want?

707
00:39:12,199 --> 00:39:13,239
I want to go to Beijing.

708
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,320
That's far.

709
00:39:15,719 --> 00:39:17,039
Have you ever traveled this far?

710
00:39:17,519 --> 00:39:18,439
I want to go

711
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:19,519
because I've never been there.

712
00:39:19,519 --> 00:39:20,519
Just let me know

713
00:39:20,519 --> 00:39:21,759
when your plan is ready.

714
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:23,360
No,

715
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:26,199
I want you to sponsor me.

716
00:39:26,199 --> 00:39:27,000
How much?

717
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:29,320
Not much.

718
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:32,639
The ticket plus the round-trip expenses

719
00:39:32,639 --> 00:39:35,639
are around 1,000 yuan.

720
00:39:39,960 --> 00:39:40,880
Dear,

721
00:39:42,079 --> 00:39:44,039
let me tell you a secret.

722
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,840
About that lottery ticket
that Zhang bought,

723
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:48,679
I bought it with him

724
00:39:48,679 --> 00:39:49,400
so...

725
00:39:52,199 --> 00:39:53,400
The fish is ready, right?

726
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:54,280
Coming.

727
00:39:57,239 --> 00:39:59,480
Men are all liars.

728
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:14,840
You're having a concert?

729
00:40:15,519 --> 00:40:16,638
Serve this for me.

730
00:40:17,239 --> 00:40:17,920
Yes.

731
00:40:24,039 --> 00:40:24,840
Mom,

732
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,880
I heard that Dad looked like Danny Chan

733
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:28,119
when he was young,

734
00:40:28,119 --> 00:40:29,000
Is that true?

735
00:40:29,519 --> 00:40:32,759
Why would you compare
your father to Danny Chan?

736
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,760
He can't even compare
to one strand of his hair.

737
00:40:35,199 --> 00:40:35,960
What do you mean?

738
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:37,920
Yingzi, listen.

739
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:39,400
Danny Chan

740
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:40,039
used to be

741
00:40:40,039 --> 00:40:42,840
the prince charming

742
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:43,960
in many girls' hearts.

743
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:46,440
He was handsome,

744
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:48,199
and he sang passionately.

745
00:40:48,199 --> 00:40:49,719
Our female classmates secretly agreed

746
00:40:49,719 --> 00:40:50,840
that someday

747
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:52,079
they would definitely

748
00:40:52,079 --> 00:40:54,320
go to his concert
and listen to him sing live.

749
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:59,440
Yet, I never got to listen to it
as I got old,

750
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:01,519
it has become a lifelong regret for me.

751
00:41:02,159 --> 00:41:04,480
How tormenting!

752
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:05,960
Mom,

753
00:41:06,719 --> 00:41:07,840
do you wish your daughter

754
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:09,840
to have lifelong regrets just like you?

755
00:41:10,159 --> 00:41:11,199
What do you mean?

756
00:41:12,079 --> 00:41:14,280
Stefanie Sun will have a concert
in Beijing next month.

757
00:41:14,519 --> 00:41:15,959
Can you sponsor me a ticket?

758
00:41:17,119 --> 00:41:17,920
No.

759
00:41:19,239 --> 00:41:21,400
Didn't we have a good chat just now?

760
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:22,760
You just said

761
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:24,000
it was a huge pity for you

762
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,000
that you never saw Danny Chan.

763
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:27,119
Can't you understand my feelings?

764
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:30,039
I was only halfway done
with my sentence.

765
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:31,480
Sure.

766
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:34,280
It was indeed a regret
that I never saw Danny Chan,

767
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:35,960
but what I regret more is

768
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:37,599
because I was addicted
to listening to music,

769
00:41:37,599 --> 00:41:38,880
I did not put much effort
in my studies.

770
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,559
I didn't even get into college.

771
00:41:41,039 --> 00:41:42,199
I will definitely go...

772
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:44,920
Not only did I not get into college,

773
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:45,960
I also met your father,

774
00:41:45,960 --> 00:41:48,320
the counterfeit version of Danny Chan.

775
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:49,880
With a small ponytail

776
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:51,639
and singing a couple of lines
of a Cantonese song,

777
00:41:51,639 --> 00:41:53,840
he managed to win my heart.

778
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:56,199
Tell me, don't you think
idolizing celebrities can be harmful?

779
00:41:57,039 --> 00:41:57,880
Listen,

780
00:41:57,880 --> 00:42:01,400
there's no way I'm going to
let my daughter make the same mistake.

781
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:07,159
Even Danny Chan doesn't help.

782
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:14,199
Mom, this is my monthly exam result.

783
00:42:14,199 --> 00:42:15,360
I did particularly well this time,

784
00:42:15,639 --> 00:42:16,239
I got first place.

785
00:42:17,199 --> 00:42:18,159
Son,

786
00:42:18,159 --> 00:42:19,760
the nearer you are to
the third year of high school,

787
00:42:19,760 --> 00:42:21,360
the more potential you seem to have.

788
00:42:24,920 --> 00:42:25,880
Are you tired, Mom?

789
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:28,519
Let me reward you
by treating you to a meal outside.

790
00:42:28,519 --> 00:42:29,279
What do you think?

791
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:31,639
Mom, I don't want to eat outside.

792
00:42:31,639 --> 00:42:32,840
What do you want, then?

793
00:42:33,719 --> 00:42:34,880
I'm thinking...

794
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,719
I want to go to Beijing.

795
00:42:38,239 --> 00:42:39,559
Beijing is good.

796
00:42:39,559 --> 00:42:42,159
You should try Qingbei University
based on your result.

797
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:44,039
If you get in,

798
00:42:44,039 --> 00:42:45,239
I will follow you there.

799
00:42:45,239 --> 00:42:46,239
I'm not talking about the future,

800
00:42:46,239 --> 00:42:47,360
I mean now.

801
00:42:48,719 --> 00:42:50,119
Why do you want to go to Beijing now?

802
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,920
Me, Yingzi, Jiang Yi, and the others

803
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:54,239
agreed to go for a Beijing trip.

804
00:42:56,119 --> 00:42:58,480
Listen, have you ever traveled far?

805
00:42:58,480 --> 00:42:59,559
That is precisely the reason

806
00:42:59,559 --> 00:43:00,519
I want to go.

807
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:02,320
Let me ask you again,

808
00:43:03,119 --> 00:43:05,000
have you considered safety issues?

809
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:07,280
Have you considered the feasibility
of this matter?

810
00:43:07,280 --> 00:43:08,719
Does Guan Chao's family have money?

811
00:43:08,719 --> 00:43:10,360
There's also Yifei.

812
00:43:10,360 --> 00:43:10,920
If you go,

813
00:43:10,920 --> 00:43:11,880
how about Grandma?

814
00:43:12,159 --> 00:43:13,800
Even if I agree,

815
00:43:13,800 --> 00:43:15,800
will Fang Mingyu's mother

816
00:43:15,800 --> 00:43:17,679
and Huang Yingzi's mother agree?

817
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:21,719
Mom, just let me go.

818
00:43:21,719 --> 00:43:23,159
Stop it. No way.

819
00:43:24,760 --> 00:43:25,519
Mom,

820
00:43:25,519 --> 00:43:27,399
I want to leave Hangtian City

821
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:28,199
and visit Beijing with my friends.

822
00:43:28,199 --> 00:43:28,639
What's wrong with that?

823
00:43:28,639 --> 00:43:29,400
Can't I?

824
00:43:30,440 --> 00:43:32,480
Are you blaming me now?

825
00:43:32,480 --> 00:43:35,320
Go ask Huang Yingzi's parents, then.

826
00:43:35,320 --> 00:43:36,440
I will not stop you

827
00:43:36,840 --> 00:43:37,800
if they agree.

828
00:43:39,960 --> 00:43:41,440
I'll get last place in the next exam.

829
00:43:42,679 --> 00:43:43,639
Brat.

830
00:43:49,039 --> 00:43:50,800
Essential items for studying
and entertainment.

831
00:43:50,800 --> 00:43:51,960
Would you mind taking a look?

832
00:43:52,400 --> 00:43:54,960
Why didn't I think of selling books?

833
00:43:54,960 --> 00:43:57,639
Must-have books for entertainment
and learning.

834
00:43:58,719 --> 00:43:59,840
Mingyu.

835
00:44:01,239 --> 00:44:03,800
I may really not be able
to go to Beijing.

836
00:44:06,639 --> 00:44:08,239
Don't be so pessimistic.

837
00:44:08,639 --> 00:44:11,280
What if Yingzi convinces her parents?

838
00:44:11,280 --> 00:44:13,360
Her parents can advise your mother

839
00:44:13,360 --> 00:44:14,440
and you'll have hope.

840
00:44:14,440 --> 00:44:16,199
Don't you know my mother?

